data.title: Blanquerna - Ramon Llull University
data.meta_description: Educational excellence and personalized attention, the best way to get where you want to go. At Blanquerna-URL we work to ensure our students have a future full of possibilities and to make their dreams come true.
data.text:
We want to make it easier for you to access the training offered by our schools, which is why we offer you various kinds of discounts.

Blanquerna-URL is waiting for you!

Are you a Blanquerna Brandlover? You can now buy products to show off Blanquerna, not only to come to the University, but also for your everyday life.

According to the 2020 AQU Survey, the employability rate for Blanquerna qualifications is 95%. This means that 95% of Blanquerna graduates find work in the specialty for which they have prepared.

We are the only private Catalan university recognized as a Campus of International Excellence (CIE). The main objective is to promote academic, teaching and research excellence in a joint commitment to social, responsible and sustainable innovation on a local and global scale.

Ramon Llull University (URL) has been ranked in the world ranking of universities under 50 years old - THE Young University Rankings - with very good results. It has achieved the 194th place worldwide and the 5th place in Spain.

Among private universities in Spain, URL is in the 1st position.

In the ranking of areas of knowledge, URL is positioned as the 1st university in Spain in Journalism and Communication, and the 3rd Catalan university in the field of Political Science (degree in International Relations).

Ramon Llull University (URL) has been ranked in the Times Higher Education (THE) World University Rankings, specifically, among the 501-600 in the world. The University is also ranked 7th in Spain and 4th in the Catalan university system. It has excelled in the area of citations in scientific publications (83.6 points out of 100) and internationally.

The URL is positioned in the 1st group of universities with the best teaching performance in Spain and 1st in Catalonia. In the general performance ranking, it appears in the 5th group of best universities in Spain with the best performance.

Four Blanquerna-URL master's degrees are among the best in Spanish universities: The master's degree in Compulsory Secondary Education and Baccalaureate Teacher Training, Vocational Training and Language Teaching, the master's degree in Advertising Strategy and Creativity, the master's degree in Educational Psychology and the master's degree in Advanced Journalism and Reporting.
